# Enhancing Sales and Supply Chain Performance through Data-Driven Insights

## Project Description
This project aims to leverage sales and supply chain performance dashboards to identify key areas for improvement and implement data-driven strategies to enhance overall performance.

## Objectives
- Improve order fulfillment rate to 20%
- Reduce average lead time from 21 days to 15 days.
- Increase average inventory turnover rate from 4.9 to 7.0.
- Reduce stock out days from 21.77 to 10 days.
- Enhance the perfect order rate from 0.89 to 0.95.

## Steps
1. Data Collection and Integration
2. Dashboard Development
3. Analysis and Insights
4. Strategy Formulation
5. Implementation
6. Continuous Monitoring
7. Documentation and Reporting

